high_descs: Turn around to the right and walk to the sink.
Pick up the tomato that is to the right of the sink.
Turn around to the right and walk to the refrigerator with the tomato in hand.
Open the refrigerator place the tomato on the shelf, close the refrigerator. Open the refrigerator, remove the tomato, close the refrigerator.
Turn to the right and walk to the microwave.
Place the tomato onto the plate that is in the microwave, shut the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool tomato into a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter with the black dishwasher ahead.
Pick up the tomato to the left of the blue coffee maker on the counter.
Turn around and walk to the black fridge on the left side.
Put the tomato inside the fridge on the second shelf from the bottom, chill it for seven seconds, remove it, and close the door.
Turn around, walk to the wall ahead and turn left to face the microwave.
Put the chilled tomato inside the microwave in between a white mug and an egg and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the counter just right of the sink
Pick up the tomato from the counter
Turn right and walk over to the fridge
Put the tomato into the fridge then remove it
Turn right and walk over to the far side of the counter where the microwave is
Put the tomato in the microwave and shut the door
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled tomato in the microwave
